Package: zoomdownloader
Version: DEB_VERSION
Architecture: all
Maintainer: DEB_MAINTAINER
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv
Description: Tonelib forum patch scraper & TUI browser
 Scrapes and browses Zoom G3n / G3Xn / G5n guitar patches
 from the Tonelib community forum. Supports uploading patches
 directly to the pedal via USB/MIDI SysEx.
